Dear {!Exhibition_Vehical_Booking__c.Internal_Registration__c}
您好！欢迎您抵青参加2025年度营销会议。我们已根据您的行程为您安排用车，详细信息如下：

用车类型：接机
发车时间：{!Exhibition_Vehical_Booking__c.Assistant_Use_Time__c}
车牌号：{!Exhibition_Vehical_Booking__c.Assistant_Vehicle_Num__c}
司机：{!Exhibition_Vehical_Booking__c.Assistant_Driver__c}
司机电话：{!Exhibition_Vehical_Booking__c.Assistant_Driver_Phone__c}
上车地点：青岛胶东国际机场
司机会举“海信”字样接机牌在行李提取出口等候您。

如您有任何疑问，请联系Becky（手机：18678919907 邮箱：songliyun1@hisense.com）

Dear {!Exhibition_Vehical_Booking__c.Internal_Registration__c}
Welcome to Qingdao to attend the 2025 Annual Marketing Meeting. We have arranged a vehicle for you according to your itinerary, details are as follows:

Type of transportation: Pick-up
Departure time: {!Exhibition_Vehical_Booking__c.Assistant_Use_Time__c}
LiLicense Plate Number: {!Exhibition_Vehical_Booking__c.Assistant_Vehicle_Num__c}
Driver: {!Exhibition_Vehical_Booking__c.Assistant_Driver__c}
Driver's Phone Number: {!Exhibition_Vehical_Booking__c.Assistant_Driver_Phone__c}
Pick up location: Qingdao Jiaodong International Airport
The driver will hold up a Hisense sign board and wait for you at the Baggage Claim Area Exit.

If you have any questions, please contact Becky at songliyun1@hisense.com or 18678919907.
